text: Cratena affinis is a species of sea slug, an aeolid nudibranch, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Facelinidae.MolluscaBase (2018). Cratena affinis (Baba, 1949). Accessed on 2018-02-17. ==Distribution== This species was described from Sagami Bay, Japan.Rudman, W.B., 2002 (November 25) Cratena affinis (Baba, 1949). [In] Sea Slug Forum.
